{"tid":1855893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護：政府智障 唔封關先係歧視本港居民","createTime":"2020-02-01T10:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T04:02:13.000Z","uid":125168,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e6601ad06d19a3e39d5037b2bf92327d34b8a24c","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"醫管局員工陣線今表決罷工 前線護士反擊林鄭：唔封關先係歧視本港居民<br />\n<br />\n獨媒<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2SayxN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2SayxN8&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=a93f2d9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2SayxN8</a>"},{"pid":"86712687ea480e54c99950452c73fd30ac4b66e9","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署：香港真普選計劃<br />\n2月1日截止，欠少少簽名，要簽爆10萬個！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=76a5e6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a>"},{"pid":"fddbd21d2de6da677f2b68650a7246e2c31d254c","tid":1855893,"uid":185045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"邏輯正確<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"61abad76ed5a56ec8e4ac12931c7010c75a7e9fb","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26e9fcbe963f9db81d168461045c51bf63342112","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"任職急症室護士的戴小姐表示，加入工會是為了與同事「一齊罷工」，向政府施壓，要求全面封關及中央處理派口罩。對於林鄭月娥昨日指封關是歧視內地旅客，她直斥：「吓？唔封關先係歧視本港居民同妄顧香港居民自身安全！」戴小姐續稱，有近一半前線員工支持罷工，而為免影響醫療服務，同事間已自發商議編排罷工期間的更表，以維持有限度緊急服務。她又指不少高層都「不敢出聲」，估計是害怕會惹來前線醫護的強烈反應，甚至將行動升級。"},{"pid":"fd715e825ba2ea99f8417a83b527deda207447fb","tid":1855893,"uid":20834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"講得好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174ec6958d8109a03e9b8f5b451e2ffebd787e0f","tid":1855893,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deba6d03eff2394939796ce544f3d319a66e6272","tid":1855893,"uid":250654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"支持醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240776eb1cf07619afbd4057142ebf1553ede27b","tid":1855893,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"淋病唔係智障<br />\n唔係點解畀其中一個仔去德國讀書諗定食兩家茶禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01081be1bcecaa4c8cd5d946c79c8a8e89d5175","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d632a47028f11031434a24479e76b1bcfcd43f0","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"張先生直言，罷工會影響病人，「一定唔理想」，但醫護不應只看眼前一日的病人，而應從整個香港的立場出發，現有資源「根本冇辦法handle咁多病人」。他又怒轟政府「封關是歧視內地人」的說法「智障」，直斥政府只會挪用對自己有利的決定，「世衞夠叫佢公佈催淚彈成分，咁佢有冇跟？新加坡封關，咁佢又有冇跟？」又批評醫管局高層將所有責任轉嫁醫護，試圖「道德綁架」，「佢哋先係始作俑者」，增加前線醫護的負擔。"},{"pid":"f515a44fb97ac3713c50c9b879f28deadb6f4560","tid":1855893,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"即時1817: <br />\n就快到七點啦！入咗嚟既每人推十下，之後其他手足接力！推到八點完場！<br />\n推完準備落街啦！<br />\n<br />\n「全城集氣撐醫護！！」今日三個行程終極懶人包！我要所有人出嚟集氣！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1854740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1854740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f77fa97551fbacf2ea4ffd8b743b964e99c5e160","tid":1855893,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"香港要負責分擔支那部分個案，以免支那醫院爆煲，只要中共政權穩定，香港死幾多人唔係考慮範圍之內"},{"pid":"fec70d2da9e24690a2d2f4a554d4652b6ae5d37c","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ceda65f16da18cf9845167899d2847009462164","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76f63532a7a82e64a462e6fdbad13dda3889aed","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f77fa97551fbacf2ea4ffd8b743b964e99c5e160","tid":1855893,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"香港要負責分擔支那部分個案，以免支那醫院爆煲，只要中共政權穩定，香港死幾多人唔係考慮範圍之內"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"港共呃唔到讀過書嘅正常人，何況醫護"},{"pid":"090dead235a2dfdd4d11284d5325951266229590","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8141d7ef6b37d85ca1d3d711b8ca23cf337512d","tid":1855893,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b76f63532a7a82e64a462e6fdbad13dda3889aed","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f77fa97551fbacf2ea4ffd8b743b964e99c5e160","tid":1855893,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"香港要負責分擔支那部分個案，以免支那醫院爆煲，只要中共政權穩定，香港死幾多人唔係考慮範圍之內"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"港共呃唔到讀過書嘅正常人，何況醫護"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"就算呃唔到<br />\n有權力就可以為所欲為啦"},{"pid":"cfd40de30deb260cbafa8ef4545b238a22febc37","tid":1855893,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"柒婆報復香港人既手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e5b6d9fb69805e64fd19e4d65b12e4d2f3e5e9","tid":1855893,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚多人香港開工番大陸住.日日來回<br />\n不如借呢次cut走埋呢班假香港人</span>"},{"pid":"2ab49b8de6b52c16af1177578948b54e5c441e9f","tid":1855893,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"📢民主黨發起全港簽名運動<br />\n支持醫護 封關救港 禁止內地人來港<br />\n<br />\n✅ 網上聯署連結: shorturl.at/iHSVZ<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎襲港，內地確診個案已經突破一萬大關，全中國擴散，香港亦已經超過14個確診個案。封關是阻止疫情擴散的重中之重的必須手段。<br />\n<br />\n內地患者源源不絕來港求醫，醫療系統無可能應付全國需求。林鄭拒封關，醫護系統爆煲，香港人人自危。醫護人員發動罷工要求封關，是保護港人下迫於無奈的一步。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我們要求政府：<br />\n<br />\n1. 支持醫護人員訴求，即時封關，於關口採取嚴厲管制入境措施，禁止內地人來港；及<br />\n<br />\n2. 提供足夠口罩及防護裝備給醫護人員，前線公務員及市民，並制訂措施禁止商人抬價。<br />\n#民主黨 #撐醫護 #罷工 #封關 #聯署 #林卓延<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"0b78b7d4f13e35f82145325c383a8ca33e689e42","tid":1855893,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:01:57.000Z","msg":"罷工人數調查<br />\nPWH <br />\n7A ~7<br />\n7B ~17<br />\n10C ~10 +10ccu 8<br />\n11A ~17<br />\n11C ～16<br />\n12B ~ 14<br />\n10LM ~20<br />\nNNU: 73<br />\n11HKLM: 23<br />\n4Eonco:~7<br />\nCIC~5<br />\n<br />\nPrivate: ~17<br />\n<br />\nolmh E3：～10<br />\n<br />\nUch <br />\n10B: ~12<br />\n12B: ~14<br />\nUCH Physio: 40<br />\n<br />\nPY ICU: ~33<br />\n<br />\nYCH<br />\nOT: 24<br />\nTSSU: 6<br />\n<br />\nKWH<br />\nE4 12<br />\nN3 18<br />\nN4 27<br />\nE2 3<br />\nSurg 10<br />\nE10 may SL<br />\nE8 6-7<br />\nN8 7<br />\nN11 10<br />\nO&amp;G 17<br />\nOT 40<br />\nICU 6<br />\n<br />\nCmc <br />\n5D 11<br />\n13B 19<br />\n11B 18<br />\n2A 3<br />\n5C 2<br />\n13A 18<br />\n12A 11<br />\nOT 38<br />\n9AB 14<br />\n<br />\nPMH<br />\nOT 33<br />\n<br />\nQEH<br />\nO&amp;T ~29<br />\n<br />\nPOH <br />\nOT 24<br />\n4s 10<br />\n4n 10<br />\n5s 11<br />\n5c 17<br />\n5n 14<br />\n6s 7RN + 1clerk<br />\n6c 12<br />\n6n unknown<br />\n7n 5<br />\n8s 9<br />\n8c unknown<br />\n8n 7<br />\n<br />\nTSWH HD 4RN+3HCA<br />\nTSWH AED 20<br />\nTSWH 7B 10<br />\nTSWH 5A 8<br />\n<br />\nTMH A6 10<br />\nTMH C6 11<br />\nTMH C9 11<br />\nTMH D5 5<br />\nTMG D6 13<br />\nTMH D7 12<br />\nTMH D9 7<br />\nTMH F1 12<br />\nTMH Radiographers 31<br />\nTMH PT 50<br />\nTHM CCU 20<br />\n<br />\nHKCH 31<br />\n<br />\n😎<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵更多人罷工💋話比人知罷先係大！多！數！"},{"pid":"8cab9c37036ac9bee3a6ebf5f801be94931322d8","tid":1855893,"uid":322412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T04:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97ZKWvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97ZKWvm.jpg&h=9a8e5a99&s={SIZE}\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"86712687ea480e54c99950452c73fd30ac4b66e9","tid":1855893,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署：香港真普選計劃<br />\n2月1日截止，欠少少簽名，要簽爆10萬個！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Iq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=76a5e6b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a>"}}